UID:10028095-1773838800-1773844200@www.phinneycenter.org
SUMMARY:Bar Stories Legacy
DESCRIPTION:Bar Stories Legacy Project\, hosted in Seattle by Nick Vega and Rebecca Lambert\, is coming to the GSC. Featuring your stories – brought to life! The show offers three participation options: Featured Storytellers with 7-8 minute slots\, On-the-Fly Storytellers with 3-minute tales\, and In-Your-Seat one-minute stories. Each story captures authentic\, real-life moments—hilarious\, dramatic\, or touching—shared in a conversational style. After each tale\, the audience engages in a brief Q&A. The only rule is kindness and respect. As a bonus\, every storyteller receives a free professional recording of their performance. Pull up a chair and share your story—it’s waiting to be told! RSVP: 206.297.0875.
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/bar-stories-legacy/
LOCATION:Greenwood Senior Center\, 525 N. 85th St.\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103\, United States
CATEGORIES:Events,GSC Featured,Senior Events
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://media.phinneycenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2025/05/20144827/bar_stories.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Greenwood Senior Center":MAILTO:gsc@phinneycenter.org
END:VEVENT
