SUMMARY:CPR\, First Aid & HIV Certification
DESCRIPTION:Learn first aid\, infant\, child and adult CPR\, HIV and bloodborne pathogens\, with a focus on injury prevention and safety. Meets L/I WISHA-WAC safety standards. Certificates issued at end of class. \nCan you provide first aid in emergencies\, locate and take care of injuries\, help a choking infant or child and stop cardiac arrest? Learn first aid\, infant\, child and adult CPR\, HIV and bloodborne pathogens\, with a focus on injury prevention and safety. \nModified to meet COVID-19 safety requirements (hands-on only\, no mouth-to mouth). \nMeets L/I WISHA-WAC safety standards. Certificates issued at end of class. \nTaught by Ken Norris\, Retired Firefighter. \nLocation: Upper Blue Building\, Room 7.
URL:https://www.phinneycenter.org/event/cpr-first-aid-hiv-certification-4/
LOCATION:Phinney Center Campus\, 6532 Phinney Ave. N.\, Seattle\, WA\, 98103\, United States
CATEGORIES:Classes,Services
