SUMMARY:Holi Celebration
DESCRIPTION:Holi – “the festival of color” or “the festival of love” – celebrates spring\, connection\, and the triumph of good over evil. Come together to celebrate this traditional Indian festival with music\, dancing\, food\, and color!
